default.description: Flag indicating if this group membership is the default one.

url.description: URL pointing to the group membership resource.

user_id.description: The unique identifier of the user associated with this group membership.

updated_at.description: Timestamp indicating when the group membership was last updated.

group_id.description: The unique identifier of the group this membership belongs to.

created_at.description: Timestamp indicating when the group membership was created.

id.description: The unique identifier of the group membership.
